        "Dock shutdown threatens shortages and sparks street-level unrest",
        "Marrow surveyors and Saints lookouts clash over who controls marked buildings"
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "Vice Bureau Raid on the Velvet Lark",
      "description": "The Vice Bureau schedules a high-profile raid on the Velvet Lark to feed the papers and squeeze the Harbor Saints, while Detective Halden secretly tries to warn Eve without exposing his own corruption and marriage.",
      "tensions": [
        "Eve risks arrest, blackmail, or becoming an informant if caught mid-courier work",
        "Saints suspect the club is leaking and may punish staff preemptively",
        "A Marrow Society intermediary offers Eve a new identity in exchange for a single delivery through the fog"
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```

